<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <script src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.9.1.min.js"></script>
    <title>선바람-로그인페이지</title>
    <style>
        * {
            font-family: "제주명조";
        }

        .wrapper {
            margin-left: -100px;
            width: 1500px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .container {
            width: 1300px;
            height: 100px;
            position: absolute;
            z-index: 100;
            margin-left: 100px;
        }
        /*상단메뉴*/
        .my_menu {
            width: 360px;
            height: 30px;
            margin-left: 940px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            position: absolute;
            z-index: 2;
        }

            .my_menu > ul {
                height: 30px;
                padding: 0;
            }

                .my_menu > ul > a {
                    color: black;
                    text-decoration: none;
                    float: left;
                    margin-top: -15px;
                    font-size: 10pt;
                }

                    .my_menu > ul > a > li {
                        list-style: none;
                        height: 30px;
                        width: 90px;
                        line-height: 30px;
                    }

                        .my_menu > ul > a > li:hover {
                            text-decoration: underline;
                        }

        /*메인메뉴*/
        .menu {
            width: 1300px;
            height: 70px;
            background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
            position: absolute;
            margin-top: 30px;
            z-index: 10;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 6px 0px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .logo {
            width: 250px;
            height: 70px;
            float: left;
            margin-right: 246px;
            text-align: center;
            display: block;
        }

            .logo a > img {
                width: auto;
                height: 100%;
                display: inline;
            }

        .nav {
            width: 804px;
            height: 70px;
            float: left;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .nav > ul {
                width: 804px;
                height: 70px;
                list-style: none;
                margin-top: 0px;
                padding: 0;
            }

                .nav > ul > a {
                    color: black;
                    text-decoration: none;
                    float: left;
                    font-size: 15pt;
                }

                    .nav > ul > a > li {
                        line-height: 70px;
                        width: 134px;
                    }

                        .nav > ul > a > li:hover {
                            background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
                            color: white;
                            height: 70px;
                        }
        /*메인메뉴-서브메뉴*/
        .submenu {
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0;
            width: 134px;
            height: 250px;
            background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
            box-shadow: 0px 3px 6px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
            display: none;
        }

            .submenu li {
                list-style: none;
                text-decoration: none;
                line-height: 50px;
                color: black;
                font-size: 13pt;
            }

                .submenu li:hover {
                    color: pink;
                    text-decoration: underline;
                }

        .comment {
            width: 1300px;
            height: 270px;
            background-color: rgb(64,78,110);
            margin-top: 100px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .comment img {
                width: 60px;
                height: 60px;
                margin-top: 60px;
            }

            .comment p {
                color: white;
                font-size: 18pt;
                margin: 20px auto;
            }

        .info_title {
            width: 1298px;
            height: 40px;
            background-color: rgb(245,245,245);
            border-left: 1px solid #444444;
            border-right: 1px solid #444444;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .info_title p {
                margin: 0;
                font-size: 14pt;
                line-height: 40px;
                font-weight: bolder;
            }

        .info {
            border: 1px solid black;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid #444444;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            text-align: center;
        }

        th, td {
            border: 1px solid #444444;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 13pt;
            font-weight: lighter;
        }

        button {
            width: 500px;
            height: 60px;
            background-color: rgb(132,162,187);
            border-style: none;
            margin-left: 400px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            border-radius: 7px;
        }

            button > a {
                font-size: 15pt;
                color: white;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            button:hover {
                background-color: rgb(103,128,148);
            }
    </style>
</head>
@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Http;
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="my_menu">
                <ul>
                    @if (Context.Session.GetInt32("User_Login_Key") == null)
                    {
                        <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Login"><li>로그인</li></a>
                        <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Sign_up"><li>회원가입</li></a>
                        <a href="#"><li>장바구니</li></a>
                        <a href="#"><li>주문조회</li></a>
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Logout"><li>로그아웃</li></a>
                        <a href="#"><li>장바구니</li></a>
                        <a href="#"><li>주문조회</li></a>
                    }
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="menu">
                <div class="logo">
                    <a href="/Web/Main"><img src="https://ifh.cc/g/vjMHmu.png" alt="로고"></a>
                </div>
                <div class="nav">
                    <ul>
                        <a href="#"><li>남자한복</li></a>
                        <a href="#"><li>여자한복</li></a>
                        <a href="#"><li>남아한복</li></a>
                        <a href="#"><li>여아한복</li></a>
                        <a href="#">
                            <li>
                                한복소품
                                <ul class="submenu">
                                    <li>노리개</li>
                                    <li>모자</li>
                                    <li>가방</li>
                                    <li>헤어</li>
                                    <li>보자기</li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#"><li>한복대여</li></a>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="comment">
                <img src="https://ifh.cc/g/N3J61i.png" alt="check">
                <p>선바람을 이용해주셔서 감사합니다.</p>
                <p>고객님,주문이 완료되었습니다.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="info_title">
                <p>주문정보</p>
            </div>
            <table border="1">
                <th>구매자 번호</th>
                <th>상품명</th>
                <th>주문일자</th>
                <th>상품금액</th>
                <tr>
                    <!-- 첫번째 줄 시작 -->

                    <td style="padding-top:40px; padding-bottom:40px; font-size:15pt; font-weight:bold;"> @ViewData["User_No"]</td>
                    <td style="padding-top:40px; padding-bottom:40px; font-size:15pt; font-weight:bold;"> @ViewData["Product_Name"]</td>
                    <td style="padding-top:40px; padding-bottom:40px; font-size:15pt; font-weight:bold;"> @ViewData["Order_Time"]</td>
                    <td style="padding-top:40px; padding-bottom:40px; font-size:15pt; font-weight:bold;"> @ViewData["Product_Cost"]</td>

                </tr><!-- 첫번째 줄 끝 -->
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="4">주문내역 확인은 배송/마이페이지의 "주문/배송조회"에서 하실 수 있습니다.</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <button type="button"><a href="/Web/Main">홈화면으로 돌아가기</a></button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        $(".nav>ul>a>li").mouseover(function () {
            $(this).children(".submenu").stop().slideDown();
        });
        $(".nav>ul>a>li").mouseleave(function () {
            $(this).children(".submenu").stop().slideUp();
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
